	* Finish rework of the compositor, which should fix quite few bugs
	  and improve performance (by discarding damages of covered
	  windows, for example), unredirecting fullscreen overrides seems
	  to work fine which gives a huge performance boost on fullscreen
	  games, fixes translucent xscreensaver window, rework the
	  NET_ACTIVE_WINDOW message handling to improve focus passing (see
	  this thread on the ML
