2003-01-10 10:55  xfce

	* BEWARE: Changed the default mode to *not* fork at startup. Use
	  "xfwm --daemon" to get the daemon mode (this is because usually,
	  window managers aren't supposed to turn themselves into daemon
	  and that cause problems to some)

