2002-05-07 22:22  xfce

	* Use Jens' idea about gtk style to set color/fonts on window
	  decorations.
	  
	  Something like :
	  
	  style "titlebar"
	  {
	  font_name = "Sans 14"
	  }
	  
	  widget "xfwm" style "titlebar"
	  
	  does the trick now.

